    <description>Double Commander dark and minimal configuration settings.

## Features

- Dark colors
- Filter files by typing
- Configurable icon and font size
- English language
- Minimal interface
- Some defaults changed (see package code for complete list)

## Package Parameters

- `/IconSize` - Set file list icon size, by default 16
- `/FontSize` - Set file list font size, by default 12

## Notes

- Also available for Total Commander: [tcc-unlit](https://chocolatey.org/packages/tcc-unlit)

